1073B 3 1073
1 Section 4. There is appropriated $150,000 from the general fund, to the Department of
2 Health, for grants to school districts and accredited nonpublic schools for the purchase of
3 automated external defibrillators.
4 Section 5. The secretary of the Department of Health shall approve vouchers and the state
5 auditor hall draw warrants to pay expenditures authorized in this Act.
6 Section 6. Any amounts appropriated in this Act not lawfully expended or obligated shall
7 revert in accordance with the procedures described in chapter 4-8.
